down and be with our mind

01:17:29.550 --> 01:17:30.930 align:middle line:90%
in this intimate kind of way.

01:17:30.930 --> 01:17:33.490 align:middle line:90%


01:17:33.490 --> 01:17:35.410 align:middle line:90%
>> There's no external input.

01:17:35.410 --> 01:17:36.660 align:middle line:90%
