01:18:08.660 --> 01:18:14.370 align:middle line:90%


01:18:14.370 --> 01:18:17.640 align:middle line:84%
But I'd realized that the source
of all my pain and suffering

01:18:17.640 --> 01:18:19.670 align:middle line:90%
