01:18:19.670 --> 01:18:22.320 align:middle line:90%
And it comes from my mind.

01:18:22.320 --> 01:18:24.300 align:middle line:84%
And that's the
same for everybody.

01:18:24.300 --> 01:18:27.688 align:middle line:84%
